This directory contains Bluetooth hardware test tool source code.

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
It provides a test UI from adb shell command for Bluetooth hardware test.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================

It needs the following libs from AOSP:
1. libdl.so

and the following libs from MediaTek:
1. liblog.so

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'vendor/mediatek/libs' folder.


HOW TO USE IT?
==============

Files in this directory is used to
1. Generate a executable binary named 'autobt', which can be runned in adb shell.
2. Generate a library named 'libbluetooth_hw_test.so', which provides the actual command function for autobt test tool.


All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..

